# Light Vulpes 2.0 — Risograph Editorial
# Derived from: vulpes-theme-lab/themes/light-vulpes-v2/palette.toml
# Reference: riso pink ink on uncoated cream stock + newsprint editorial hierarchy

# Surface — pure white.
# Mirrors the dark theme's #000000 OLED black (purest possible surface).
# v2.5: the riso-cream-paper concept (#f4ede4) was over-clever and killed the
# contrast punch. Returning to white. Warm tones live on raised surfaces
# (selection, diff bgs) where they step UP from white as design accent,
# not as the base. Verified: ink ramp, accents, teal comments, diff palette
# all pass AA against #ffffff with more headroom than against cream.
background           = #ffffff
foreground           = #1a0f14
cursor-color         = #d6004c
selection-background = #ebe2d6
selection-foreground = #1a0f14

